1
00:00:18,416 --> 00:00:19,875
- Fukuhara: AKIHISA YOSHII...

2
00:00:19,958 --> 00:00:21,166
A PECULIAR YOUNG MAN

3
00:00:21,250 --> 00:00:23,666
WHO IS QUITE PARTICULAR ABOUT
THINGS HE DOES.

4
00:00:23,750 --> 00:00:24,958
- Akihisa: DOWN THE HATCH!

5
00:00:25,041 --> 00:00:26,250
( sipping )

6
00:00:27,791 --> 00:00:29,333
NOTHING LIKE SALT WATER SOUP.

7
00:00:29,416 --> 00:00:31,166
AND I GOT SUGAR WATER
FOR DESSERT...

8
00:00:31,250 --> 00:00:33,083
I'M GOING ALL OUT TONIGHT.

9
00:00:33,166 --> 00:00:34,708
- THE DEGREE TO WHICH HE
