17
00:00:55,583 --> 00:00:57,666
- ( singing in Japanese )

18
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:24,500
- Fukuhara: AKIRA YOSHII.
E CUP.

19
00:02:24,583 --> 00:02:27,583
SHE IS AKIHISA'S SISTER
AND LIVES ABROAD.

20
00:02:27,666 --> 00:02:30,875
- WHY DID YOU COME HERE
DRESSED LIKE THAT, AKIRA?

21
00:02:30,958 --> 00:02:33,750
- WHY IN THE WORLD ARE YOU
YELLING AT ME RIGHT NOW, AKI?

22
00:02:33,833 --> 00:02:35,458
YOU'RE BEING SILLY.

23
00:02:35,541 --> 00:02:37,166
- SAYS THE GIRL WEARING A ROBE.

24
00:02:37,250 --> 00:02:39,958
- IF YOU'D SHUT UP, THEN I COULD
TELL YOU WHY I'M WEARING THIS.

25
00:02:40,041 --> 00:02:42,916
JUST SO YOU KNOW, I ACTUALLY
HAVE A VERY GOOD REASON.

26
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,541
- I'M SORRY...

27
00:02:44,625 --> 00:02:45,583
PLEASE GO AHEAD.

28
00:02:47,291 --> 00:02:50,291
- YOU SEE, I HAD TO CARRY MY
HEAVY LUGGAGE FROM THE AIRPORT

29
00:02:50,375 --> 00:02:51,750
ALL THE WAY TO THE TRAIN STATION

30
00:02:51,833 --> 00:02:54,958
WITHOUT ANY AIR
CONDITIONING AT ALL.

31
00:02:55,041 --> 00:02:56,458
WHEN I FINALLY
MADE IT ON THE TRAIN,

32
00:02:56,541 --> 00:02:59,541
I WAS ABSOLUTELY DISGUSTED
TO SEE HOW SWEATY I'D BECOME.

33
00:03:00,208 --> 00:03:01,416
- MM-HMM.

34
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:03,583
- WELL I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU
IN SUCH A LONG TIME,

35
00:03:03,666 --> 00:03:05,875
I WANTED TO MAKE SURE
I LOOKED MY BEST.

36
00:03:05,958 --> 00:03:07,750
I WOULDN'T WANT YOU
TO THINK BAD OF ME.

37
00:03:08,458 --> 00:03:10,000
- MM-HMM.

38
00:03:10,083 --> 00:03:12,708
- IN ORDER TO TAKE CARE OF THE
SWEAT, I CHANGED INTO A BATHROBE

39
