BECAUSE THEY'RE SO
HIGHLY ABSORBENT.

40
00:03:14,958 --> 00:03:16,583
- WHAT? THAT'S MESSED UP!

41
00:03:16,666 --> 00:03:19,291
- THIS WAY I WAS ABLE TO REUNITE
WITH MY BABY BROTHER

42
00:03:19,375 --> 00:03:21,250
WHILE MAINTAINING THE
SWEAT-FREE APPEARANCE

43
00:03:21,333 --> 00:03:23,041
OF A DIGNIFIED, OLDER SISTER.

44
00:03:23,125 --> 00:03:24,875
- THAT'S EVEN MORE MESSED UP!

45
00:03:24,958 --> 00:03:27,375
- IT'S A GOOD THING
THE TRAIN WAS RATHER EMPTY.

46
00:03:27,458 --> 00:03:28,666
IF IT HAD BEEN MORE CROWDED,

47
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:30,791
I WOULD HAVE BEEN THOROUGHLY
EMBARRASSED.

48
00:03:30,875 --> 00:03:33,000
- WAIT... WHERE DID YOU CHANGE?

49
00:03:35,541 --> 00:03:37,666
- YOU SHOULD KNOW.
THE REASON I CAME BACK

50
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:39,166
WAS TO TAKE CARE OF
SOMETHING IMPORTANT.

51
00:03:39,250 --> 00:03:40,416
- ( gasps )

52
00:03:40,500 --> 00:03:42,416
- I NEED TO INVESTIGATE
HOW YOU'VE BEEN HANDLING

53
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:44,583
BEING ALONE
FOR THE PAST FEW MONTHS.

54
00:03:44,666 --> 00:03:47,041
THEN I CAN DETERMINE WHETHER
OR NOT I SHOULD ALLOW YOU

55
00:03:47,125 --> 00:03:48,875
TO CONTINUE
LIVING BY YOURSELF.

56
00:03:48,958 --> 00:03:50,250
- WHAT?

57
00:03:50,333 --> 00:03:51,583
- WHEN YOU FIRST
STARTED STAYING HERE

58
00:03:51,666 --> 00:03:53,541
WITHOUT ANY ADULT SUPERVISION,

59
00:03:53,625 --> 00:03:56,166
