TO FOLLOW.

60
00:03:56,250 --> 00:03:58,791
I'M ASSUMING YOU STILL REMEMBER
WHAT THEY WERE.

61
00:03:58,875 --> 00:04:01,166
- ARE YOU GONNA BE MAD
IF I SAY NO?

62
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:03,000
- OF COURSE I WON'T.

63
00:04:03,083 --> 00:04:05,041
- WELL, GOOD...
IN THAT CASE, I ...

64
00:04:05,125 --> 00:04:07,291
- WHY GET MAD WHEN I CAN
JUST GIVE YOU A KISS?

65
00:04:07,375 --> 00:04:09,250
- REMEMBER THEM BOTH!

66
00:04:09,333 --> 00:04:11,333
- AND THE KISS I HAVE IN
MIND WILL RUIN MY CHANCES

67
00:04:11,416 --> 00:04:12,916
OF EVER GETTING MARRIED.

68
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:15,125
- THAT IS NOT EVEN
A LITTLE FUNNY!

69
00:04:15,208 --> 00:04:16,791
- IT REALLY ISN'T.

70
00:04:16,875 --> 00:04:19,750
RELAX. I'M THE ONE
WHO'LL DIE ALONE.

71
00:04:19,833 --> 00:04:21,458
- HOW AM I
SUPPOSED TO RELAX?

72
00:04:21,541 --> 00:04:22,666
- THAT'S A GOOD POINT.

73
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:24,416
I MEAN, YOU'LL SPEND
THE REST OF YOUR LIFE

74
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:26,375
FEELING GUILTY FOR WHAT
YOU'VE PUT YOUR POOR,

75
00:04:26,458 --> 00:04:27,750
SPINSTER SISTER THROUGH.

76
00:04:27,833 --> 00:04:30,083
- I REMEMBER THEM, I SWEAR.
PLEASE STOP THIS.

77
00:04:30,166 --> 00:04:32,250
- GOOD. THEN WHY DON'T YOU
TELL ME WHAT THEY ARE.

78
00:04:32,333 --> 00:04:34,541
- UM, THEY'RE, UH...

79
00:04:34,625 --> 00:04:36,708
- OH, AKI. CLOSE YOUR EYES.

80
00:04:36,791 --> 00:04:38,041
- ( screams )

81
00:04:38,125 --> 00:04:40,000
I CAN ONLY PLAY VIDEO GAMES
THIRTY MINUTES A DAY

82
00:04:40,083 --> 00:04:42,291
AND ILLICIT SEXUAL RELATIONSHIPS
ARE FORBIDDEN!

83
00:04:42,375 --> 00:04:43,458
- I'M SO SORRY.

84
00:04:43,541 --> 00:04:44,833
- WAS I WRONG?

85
00:04:44,916 --> 00:04:46,958
- NO, YOU'RE RIGHT, I
JUST CAN'T KISS YOU NOW.

86
00:04:47,041 --> 00:04:49,041
- YOU SHOULDN'T BE
SORRY FOR THAT!

87
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,125
- IT'S A LOT CLEANER
THAN I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE.

88
00:04:53,208 --> 00:04:55,458
- WHY? I'VE NEVER REALLY
BEEN THAT MESSY.

89
00:04:55,541 --> 00:04:58,291
- YES, BUT AS THEY SAY,
YOU'RE "AT THAT AGE".

90
00:04:58,375 --> 00:05:00,000
I WAS EXPECTING
YOUR ROOM TO BE BURIED

91
00:05:00,083 --> 00:05:02,500
UNDERNEATH TWO THOUSAND
DIRTY BOOKS BY NOW.

92
00:05:02,583 --> 00:05:04,583
- I CAN'T AFFORD
TWO THOUSAND DIRTY BOOKS!

93
00:05:04,666 --> 00:05:07,583
- SO BASICALLY,
YOU HAVE AT LEAST ONE.

94
00:05:07,666 --> 00:05:09,041
A DEDUCTION OF 20 POINTS

95
00:05:09,125 --> 00:05:11,500
FOR A SEMI-ILLICIT SEXUAL
RELATIONSHIP.

96
00:05:11,583 --> 00:05:13,083
- WHAT ARE THE POINTS FOR?

97
00:05:13,166 --> 00:05:15,125
- I'M SCORING YOU
BASED ON THOSE CONDITIONS

98
00:05:15,208 --> 00:05:18,083
TO SEE IF YOU'VE EARNED THE
RIGHT TO CONTINUE LIVING ALONE.

99
00:05:18,166 --> 00:05:20,208
FOR THE FINAL SCORE,
I'LL AVERAGE EVERYTHING HERE

100
00:05:20,291 --> 00:05:22,083
WITH YOUR NEXT TEST
AT SCHOOL.

101
00:05:22,166 --> 00:05:23,708
- GREAT. NOW I HAVE TO
MAKE SURE I GET

102
00:05:23,791 --> 00:05:26,333
AT LEAST TWENTY EXTRA POINTS
ON MY MIDTERM EXAM.

103
00:05:26,416 --> 00:05:28,541
THAT WAY IT WILL CANCEL OUT
THOSE POINTS.

104
00:05:28,625 --> 00:05:30,333
- DON'T GET AHEAD
OF YOURSELF, YET.

105
00:05:30,416 --> 00:05:32,333
ANY OTHER ILLICIT
SEXUAL RELATIONSHIPS

106
00:05:32,416 --> 00:05:33,375
I SHOULD KNOW ABOUT?

107
00:05:33,458 --> 00:05:35,416
- IF SO, WHAT WOULD
THAT SCORE BE?

108
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:37,458
- IF YOU'RE CAUGHT
HOLDING HANDS WITH A GIRL,

109
00:05:37,541 --> 00:05:38,541
SUBTRACT ONE HUNDRED POINTS.

110
00:05:38,625 --> 00:05:40,416
- ONE HUNDRED POINTS?

111
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:42,083
- IF YOU WERE TO TAKE GIRLS
OUT TO THE MOVIES,

112
00:05:42,166 --> 00:05:43,708
OR TREAT THEM TO CREPES,

113
00:05:43,791 --> 00:05:46,208
OR EVEN IF THEY MAKE
YOU LUNCH OR WAFFLES

114
00:05:46,291 --> 00:05:47,791
OR ANYTHING TO THAT EFFECT,

115
00:05:47,875 --> 00:05:49,791
THAT WOULD BE MINUS FIFTY
THOUSAND POINTS.

116
00:05:49,875 --> 00:05:51,958
- ( muffled grunting )
- Akira: WHAT'S THE MATTER?

117
00:05:52,041 --> 00:05:53,708
- OH! NOTHING!

118
00:05:53,791 --> 00:05:56,166
I UNDERSTAND YOU'RE
A HEALTHY YOUNG MAN.

119
00:05:56,250 --> 00:05:58,083
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT YOU
DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO

120
00:05:58,166 --> 00:05:59,375
WITH YOUR BODY YET.

121
00:05:59,458 --> 00:06:01,583
- HOLD ON A MINUTE,
I NEVER SAID THAT.

122
00:06:01,666 --> 00:06:04,000
- DON'T WORRY. I'LL ALLOW YOU
A LITTLE FUN.

123
00:06:04,083 --> 00:06:06,000
ILLICIT SEXUAL
RELATIONSHIPS WITH GIRLS

124
00:06:06,083 --> 00:06:07,166
ARE AGAINST THE RULES.

125
00:06:07,250 --> 00:06:09,666
BUT ILLICIT SEXUAL
RELATIONSHIPS WITH GUYS,

126
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:11,041
THAT'S PERFECTLY FINE.

127
00:06:11,125 --> 00:06:12,500
- IT IS NOT PERFECTLY FINE!

128
00:06:12,583 --> 00:06:14,333
AND QUIT SAYING ILLICIT
SEXUAL RELATIONSHIPS!

129
00:06:14,416 --> 00:06:16,583
YOU'RE CREEPING ME OUT!

130
00:06:17,791 --> 00:06:20,208
- OH, STAR LIGHT. STAR BRIGHT.

131
00:06:20,291 --> 00:06:21,625
- NOT GOOD.

132
00:06:21,708 --> 00:06:24,708
YOUR SCORES ARE MUCH WORSE THAN
I EXPECTED THEM TO BE.

133
00:06:24,791 --> 00:06:27,291
- I TRIED REALLY HARD
IN MY OWN WAY.

134
00:06:27,375 --> 00:06:29,958
- TRYING HARD IS ONLY
A MEANS TO AN END.

135
00:06:30,041 --> 00:06:33,250
IF ALL YOU DO IS TRY WITHOUT
EVER ACCOMPLISHING ANYTHING,

136
00:06:33,333 --> 00:06:34,958
WHAT'S THE POINT,
LITTLE BROTHER?

137
00:06:35,041 --> 00:06:37,708
FAILING IS FAILING
NO MATTER HOW YOU LOOK AT IT.

138
00:06:37,791 --> 00:06:39,583
- THANKS. THAT'S JUST
WHAT I WANTED TO HEAR.

139
00:06:39,666 --> 00:06:42,291
- GET BETTER GRADES
AND I WON'T HAVE TO NAG YOU.

140
00:06:42,375 --> 00:06:44,416
JUST ONE DECENT SCORE
WOULD BE HELPFUL.

141
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:48,041
- WELL, YOU'RE NOT PERFECT.
NOT AT EVERYTHING.

142
00:06:48,125 --> 00:06:50,333
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
- Akihisa: COOKING.

143
00:06:50,416 --> 00:06:53,375
- MAKING FOOD HAS NOTHING
TO DO WITH ACADEMICS.

144
00:06:53,458 --> 00:06:54,875
- BUT IT'S IMPORTANT FOR LIFE.

145
00:06:54,958 --> 00:06:56,833
BESIDES, THE ONLY THING
YOU'RE GOOD AT IS SCHOOL WORK.

146
00:06:56,916 --> 00:06:59,958
I'LL BE FORCED TO KISS YOU
UNTIL YOU SHUT YOUR MOUTH.

147
00:07:00,041 --> 00:07:01,875
- I'M SORRY. I WAS WRONG.

148
00:07:03,958 --> 00:07:05,958
- YUUJI. I WANT TO SEE
YOUR CELL PHONE.

149
00:07:06,041 --> 00:07:07,541
- Yuuji: WHAT FOR?

150
00:07:07,625 --> 00:07:09,416
- I SAW A SHOW LAST NIGHT
THAT SAID YOU CAN TELL

151
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:10,833
IF YOUR PARTNER'S CHEATING

152
00:07:10,916 --> 00:07:12,750
BY LOOKING FOR SPECIFIC CLUES
ON THEIR PHONE. GIVE ME.

153
00:07:12,833 --> 00:07:14,333
- HELL, NO.
( screams in pain )

154
00:07:14,416 --> 00:07:17,125
MY EYES! YOU CAN'T GIVE LASER
EYE SURGERY WITH YOUR FINGERS!

155
00:07:17,208 --> 00:07:20,125
- OH MY GOD!
- FINE, BE THAT WAY.

156
00:07:20,208 --> 00:07:21,541
I DON'T MIND TAKING IT
BY FORCE.

157
00:07:21,625 --> 00:07:23,250
- HEY! WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

158
00:07:23,333 --> 00:07:24,791
- I HEARD IT WAS SEXY
TO BE NAKED

159
00:07:24,875 --> 00:07:26,291
WITH ONLY A GUY'S SHIRT ON.

160
00:07:26,375 --> 00:07:28,250
- YEAH, THAT'S FOR CHICKS,
NOT A DUDE!

161
00:07:28,333 --> 00:07:30,416
- LET ME BE THE JUDGE.

162
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:33,458
- OKAY, I GIVE UP! TAKE IT.
YOU CAN HAVE THE PHONE!

163
00:07:33,541 --> 00:07:34,625
- ARE YOU SURE?

164
00:07:34,708 --> 00:07:36,416
- YOU DON'T HAVE TO SOUND
SO DISAPPOINTED.

165
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:38,041
- GEEZ. HERE.

166
00:07:39,666 --> 00:07:40,750
- YUUJI, YOUR EMAIL.

167
00:07:40,833 --> 00:07:42,875
YOU GET MORE FROM YOSHII
THAN FROM ME.

168
00:07:42,958 --> 00:07:44,291
- YEAH, SO WHAT?

169
00:07:44,375 --> 00:07:46,875
- THAT MEANS YOU'RE HAVING
A LOVE AFFAIR WITH YOSHII.

170
00:07:46,958 --> 00:07:48,333
- ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

171
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:52,208
- Akihisa: CAN I STAY OVERNIGHT
AT YOUR PLACE?

172
00:07:52,291 --> 00:07:55,000
I KINDA DON'T WANT TO
GO HOME TONIGHT.

173
00:07:56,416 --> 00:07:58,708
- WAIT A SEC... SHOUKO... I...
( screams )

174
00:07:58,791 --> 00:08:00,541
- TAKEN CARE OF...

175
00:08:00,625 --> 00:08:02,250
- Hideyoshi: GOOD MORNING,
AKIHISA.

176
00:08:02,333 --> 00:08:03,833
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

177
00:08:03,916 --> 00:08:06,541
IT'S WEIRD, BUT YOU LOOK A LOT
HEALTHIER THAN YOU NORMALLY DO.

178
00:08:06,625 --> 00:08:09,291
- YEAH. I GOT TO EAT
ACTUAL FOOD THIS MORNING.

179
00:08:09,375 --> 00:08:11,958
- Fukuhara: AKIHISA SOLD HIS
MANGA AND VIDEO GAMES

180
00:08:12,041 --> 00:08:13,166
TO A SECOND HAND SHOP

181
00:08:13,250 --> 00:08:15,041
AND GOT MONEY TO BUY FOOD.

182
00:08:15,125 --> 00:08:17,291
- EVEN IF IT JUST
GETS ME THROUGH AKIRA'S STAY,

183
00:08:17,375 --> 00:08:19,541
AT LEAST SHE'LL THINK
I'M TAKING CARE OF MYSELF.

184
00:08:19,625 --> 00:08:21,958
OTHERWISE, SHE'LL TAKE
MORE POINTS AWAY.

185
00:08:25,541 --> 00:08:26,666
- NO PANTS DAY, HUH?

186
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:28,833
- NO, IT'S NOT NO PANTS DAY,
YOU IDIOT!

187
00:08:28,916 --> 00:08:31,291
I GOT PUNISHED BECAUSE OF
YOUR SUPER WEIRD EMAIL.

188
00:08:31,375 --> 00:08:33,125
- THERE WAS NOTHING WEIRD
ABOUT MY EMAIL.

189
00:08:33,208 --> 00:08:35,041
- WHY DON'T YOU TRY
READING IT OUT LOUD THEN.

190
00:08:37,333 --> 00:08:39,541
- CAN I STAY OVERNIGHT
AT YOURPLACE?

191
00:08:39,625 --> 00:08:42,875
I KINDA DON'T WANT TO
GO HOME TONIGHT.

192
00:08:42,958 --> 00:08:44,958
- OF COURSE! NOW IT SEEMS
SO OBVIOUS!

193
00:08:45,041 --> 00:08:47,750
- YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED TO
EXPERIMENT UNTIL YOU'RE OLDER!

194
00:08:47,833 --> 00:08:49,166
- THAT'S JUST OBSCENE, YOSHII!

195
00:08:54,083 --> 00:08:55,166
UH...

196
00:08:56,791 --> 00:08:58,083
BAKA AND TEST!

197
00:09:01,541 --> 00:09:06,625
UH, YOSHII,
GO TO THE NURSE'S OFFICE.

198
00:09:06,708 --> 00:09:09,500
- WHY DO YOU ALWAYS THINK
I'M SICK WHEN I'M STUDYING?

199
00:09:11,791 --> 00:09:13,416
- SO WHAT HAPPENED, AKI?

200
00:09:13,500 --> 00:09:16,208
I MEAN, WHY ARE YOU
STUDYING ALL OF A SUDDEN?

201
00:09:16,291 --> 00:09:18,375
- YOU'RE ACTING
A LITTLE STRANGE TODAY.

202
00:09:18,458 --> 00:09:20,500
- REALLY? I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

203
00:09:22,791 --> 00:09:26,041
- WOW. YOU'VE GOT QUITE THE
WELL-PREPARED LUNCH TODAY.

204
00:09:26,125 --> 00:09:27,958
- I KNOW. NICE FOR A CHANGE.

205
00:09:28,041 --> 00:09:30,541
- LOOKS PRETTY GOOD.
WHO MADE THIS FOR YOU ANYWAY?

206
00:09:30,625 --> 00:09:31,791
- OH, I MADE IT.

207
00:09:31,875 --> 00:09:33,500
- Minami: LIAR.
- Mizuki: YEAH, THAT'S NOT TRUE.

208
