- WHAT? I AM NOT LYING!

209
00:09:34,958 --> 00:09:36,916
- SOMEONE SUPER TALENTED
HAD TO MAKE THIS.

210
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,500
MAYBE IT WAS YUUJI OR KOUTA.

211
00:09:38,583 --> 00:09:40,291
- TELL US THE TRUTH , AKI!
COME ON!

212
00:09:40,375 --> 00:09:42,416
- JUST CONFESS,
WHO REALLY MADE IT FOR YOU?

213
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:45,708
- I THINK I'LL JUST LEAVE IT
TO YOUR IMAGINATION.

214
00:09:45,791 --> 00:09:49,125
- AKIHISA, YOU DON'T
HAVE TO GO HOME TODAY.

215
00:09:49,208 --> 00:09:51,625
- WHY DO THE GOOD ONES
ALWAYS PLAY FOR THE OTHER TEAM?

216
00:09:51,708 --> 00:09:53,583
- NO! I REFUSE TO BELIEVE IT!

217
00:09:53,666 --> 00:09:55,333
- I'LL NEVER FORGIVE YOU!

218
00:09:55,416 --> 00:09:56,500
- WHAT'D YOU IMAGINE?

219
00:09:56,583 --> 00:09:58,250
AND WHY THE HELL
IS KUBO IN OUR CLASSROOM?

220
