- HEY, SO I WAS WONDERING,

221
00:10:00,083 --> 00:10:02,083
WHY'D YOU WANT TO STAY OVER
AT MY PLACE ANYWAY?

222
00:10:02,166 --> 00:10:03,958
- WHAT? OH, I JUST THOUGHT
WE COULD STUDY.

223
00:10:04,041 --> 00:10:04,750
- DON'T LIE TO ME.

224
00:10:04,833 --> 00:10:05,875
YOU DIDN'T LET ME FINISH!

225
00:10:05,958 --> 00:10:07,375
MIDTERMS ARE COMING UP.

226
00:10:07,458 --> 00:10:09,916
I GUESS GETTING A GROUP TOGETHER
TO STUDY ISN'T A BAD IDEA.

227
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,916
- REALLY?

228
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,208
- LET'S DO IT OVER
AT YOUR PLACE.

229
00:10:13,291 --> 00:10:16,666
- NO, NO! NOT MY PLACE! TODAY
ISN'T GOOD. NO, NOT AT ALL!

230
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:18,458
IT'S NOT GOOD AT ALL!

231
00:10:18,541 --> 00:10:20,250
- PRETTY SURE HE'S H
IDING SOMETHING.

232
00:10:20,333 --> 00:10:21,791
- SHOULD PROBABLY CHECK IT OUT.

233
00:10:21,875 --> 00:10:23,500
- GET TO THE BOTTOM OF THIS.

234
00:10:23,583 --> 00:10:26,583
- NO! YOU GOT THE WRONG IDEA!
IT'S JUST MESSY! VERY MESSY...

235
00:10:26,666 --> 00:10:28,708
- THAT'S OKAY!
I'LL HELP YOU CLEAN!

236
00:10:28,791 --> 00:10:30,416
- NO. I'LL DO IT.

237
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:33,083
NEEDS TO BE SOMETHING A GIRL
WOULDN'T WANT TO TOUCH!

238
00:10:33,166 --> 00:10:35,625
THIS MESS IS BAD.
IT'S TWO THOUSAND DIRTY BOOKS.

239
00:10:37,791 --> 00:10:38,875
- I'LL STILL HELP!

240
00:10:38,958 --> 00:10:40,041
- WE CAN GET RID OF THEM!

241
00:10:40,125 --> 00:10:41,833
- YEAH, I'M IN TOO.

242
00:10:41,916 --> 00:10:44,958
- Akihisa: DAMN IT! THAT ISN'T
WHAT YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO SAY!

243
00:10:49,125 --> 00:10:50,125
- Announcer: BAKA AND TEST.

244
00:10:53,916 --> 00:10:55,875
- SO, UH, WE'RE REALLY
DOING THIS THEN?

245
00:10:55,958 --> 00:10:58,708
- LOOK DUDE, WE JUST
WANNA KNOW WHAT YOU'RE HIDING.

246
00:10:58,791 --> 00:11:01,250
- YOU'VE BEEN ACTING
RATHER SUSPICIOUS ALL DAY.

247
00:11:01,333 --> 00:11:03,875
- Kouta: I BET HE'S GOT
A SECRET GIRLFRIEND.

248
00:11:03,958 --> 00:11:06,791
- IS THAT TRUE?
WHAT'S A SECRET GIRLFRIEND?

249
00:11:06,875 --> 00:11:08,791
- UM, YOU SHOULD ASK KOUTA.

250
00:11:08,875 --> 00:11:10,958
- CALM DOWN, MINAMI.

251
00:11:11,041 --> 00:11:12,750
YOU KNOW YOSHII WOULD NEVER
EVEN DREAM OF DATING SOMEONE

252
00:11:12,833 --> 00:11:14,875
BEHIND OUR BACKS LIKE THAT.

253
00:11:14,958 --> 00:11:17,125
- Mizuki: ISN'T THAT
RIGHT, YOSHII?

254
00:11:18,208 --> 00:11:21,708
- Akihisa: WHY ARE
YOU SQUINTING?

255
00:11:21,791 --> 00:11:23,208
- WELL, IT'S TIME TO FIND OUT

256
00:11:23,291 --> 00:11:25,000
THERE'S PROBABLY
NOTHING GOING ON.

257
00:11:25,083 --> 00:11:27,541
THAT'S YOUR CUE, AKIHISA.
OPEN THE DOOR.

258
00:11:27,625 --> 00:11:29,250
- I DON'T WANNA.

259
00:11:29,333 --> 00:11:32,458
- DO YOU WANT TO GET PANTSED
LIKE I DID? THIS IS YOUR CHOICE.

260
00:11:32,541 --> 00:11:34,625
- IF YOU COULD LOOK UP AT THE
SKY WITH TEARS IN YOUR EYES,

261
00:11:34,708 --> 00:11:35,833
THAT'D BE GREAT.

262
00:11:35,916 --> 00:11:38,291
- WHAT FOR?
SO YOU CAN PROFIT FROM MY PAIN?

263
00:11:38,375 --> 00:11:41,000
- YOU KNOW WHAT ELSE? I MEAN
TO MAKE IT MORE MARKETABLE?

264
00:11:41,083 --> 00:11:43,250
YOU SHOULD HAVE HIM UNBUTTON
HIS FIRST TWO BUTTONS.

265
00:11:43,333 --> 00:11:46,375
- I AM NOT A PRODUCT TO BE
MARKETED! FINE, I'LL DO IT!

266
00:11:46,458 --> 00:11:48,250
I'LL OPEN IT
IF YOU'LL LEAVE ME ALONE!

267
00:11:48,333 --> 00:11:50,083
- Minami, Mizuki: YOUR SHIRT?
- Akihisa: NO! THE DOOR!

268
00:11:50,166 --> 00:11:51,708
- ( Akihisa screaming
in frustration )

269
00:11:51,791 --> 00:11:54,000
I CAN'T EVEN MAKE SOMETHING UP
TO EXPLAIN THIS.

270
00:11:54,083 --> 00:11:56,583
- NO, I THINK WE KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE.

271
00:11:56,666 --> 00:11:59,125
- Kouta: I'M SO JEALOUS
I COULD KILL HIM.

272
00:11:59,208 --> 00:12:02,125
- THIS IS NOT A VERY GOOD
THING, YOSHII.

273
00:12:02,208 --> 00:12:04,916
YOU BOUGHT A BRA SIZE
THAT WOULD NEVER FIT YOU.

274
00:12:05,791 --> 00:12:07,625
SMALLER CUP WOULD BE BETTER.

275
00:12:07,708 --> 00:12:09,583
- All: SHE'S REFUSING
TO FACE IT.

276
00:12:10,625 --> 00:12:12,458
- HEY, WHAT'S THAT?

277
00:12:12,541 --> 00:12:14,291
- A COTTON PAD FOR MAKEUP,
I THINK.

278
00:12:14,375 --> 00:12:16,958
- WRONG. MUST BE A FISH CAKE.

279
00:12:17,041 --> 00:12:18,333
- All: A FISH CAKE?

280
00:12:19,750 --> 00:12:21,625
- LOOK!

281
00:12:21,708 --> 00:12:24,916
- DUDE, THAT IS DEFINITELY
SOMETHING A CHICK WOULD EAT.

282
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,500
- ( Mizuki crying )
- ARE YOU ALRIGHT, HIMEJI?

283
00:12:27,583 --> 00:12:29,458
- I CAN'T KEEP DENYING
THIS ANYMORE!

284
00:12:29,541 --> 00:12:31,791
- SERIOUSLY? UNDERWEAR
AND MAKEUP ARE OKAY.

285
00:12:31,875 --> 00:12:33,958
BUT ONE STUPID LUNCH
SENDS YOU OVER THE EDGE?

286
00:12:34,041 --> 00:12:36,708
- HELLO. I SEE WE HAVE COMPANY.

287
00:12:36,791 --> 00:12:38,375
- AN OLDER WOMAN!

288
00:12:38,458 --> 00:12:40,250
WITH... HUGE BOOBS!

289
00:12:40,333 --> 00:12:41,833
HOW CAN YOU BE SO CRUEL?

290
00:12:41,916 --> 00:12:44,333
- Minami: YOU ARE TEARING
OUT MY HEART!

291
00:12:44,416 --> 00:12:46,708
- I DON'T EVEN UNDERSTAND WHAT
YOU'RE SAYING RIGHT NOW.

292
00:12:47,833 --> 00:12:49,250
ALL RIGHT.

293
00:12:49,333 --> 00:12:52,500
I'LL TELL YOU THE TRUTH.
SHE'S MY OLDER SISTER.

294
00:12:52,583 --> 00:12:54,166
- All: YOUR SISTER?

295
00:12:54,250 --> 00:12:57,791
THAT'S RIGHT. I'M AKIRA
YOSHII. THANK YOU.

296
00:12:57,875 --> 00:12:59,416
IT'S VERY NICE OF YOU
TO BE FRIENDS

297
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:01,750
WITH MY EXTREMELY
STUPID BROTHER.

298
00:13:01,833 --> 00:13:06,083
I'M SURE IT'S NOT EASY, UNLESS
HE USUALLY ISN'T THIS RUDE.

299
00:13:06,166 --> 00:13:10,041
- WOW. SHE LOOKS NORMAL EVEN IF
SHE IS BEING MEAN. I'LL TAKE IT!

300
00:13:11,791 --> 00:13:13,958
- HEY THERE, I'M YUUJI SAKAMOTO.

301
00:13:14,041 --> 00:13:15,458
- I'M KOUTA TSUCHIYA.

302
00:13:15,541 --> 00:13:17,958
- AND I'M HIDEYOSHI KINOSHITA.

303
00:13:18,041 --> 00:13:20,916
PEOPLE USUALLY ASSUME
I'M A GIRL, BUT...

304
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:23,291
- YOU'RE A BOY, AREN'T YOU?

305
00:13:23,375 --> 00:13:26,083
YOU ARE THE ONLY ONE WHO'S
EVER RECOGNIZED ME AS A GUY.

306
00:13:26,166 --> 00:13:27,041
THAT'S AMAZING!

307
00:13:27,125 --> 00:13:28,625
- WELL, IT'S KIND OF OBVIOUS.

308
00:13:28,708 --> 00:13:31,416
THERE'S NO WAY MY STUPID, UGLY,
GOOD-FOR-NOTHING LITTLE BROTHER

309
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:34,041
WOULD BE ABLE TO GET GIRLS
TO BE FRIENDS WITH HIM.

310
00:13:34,125 --> 00:13:35,625
ALTHOUGH I MUST SAY
THE TWO OF YOU

311
00:13:35,708 --> 00:13:37,625
ARE RATHER STRANGE
LOOKING BOYS.

312
00:13:37,708 --> 00:13:39,541
- WHY ARE YOU SO RUDE
ALL OF A SUDDEN?

313
00:13:39,625 --> 00:13:41,625
GO BACK TO BEING NICE, OKAY?

314
00:13:41,708 --> 00:13:43,833
ALL THREE OF THEM ARE GIRLS!

315
00:13:43,916 --> 00:13:45,541
- HOW MANY WAYS CAN I PUT IT?

316
00:13:45,625 --> 00:13:47,083
- GIRLS? REALLY.?

317
00:13:48,583 --> 00:13:50,541
WHEN DID YOU START BRINGING
GIRLS INTO THIS HOME,

318
00:13:50,625 --> 00:13:52,791
AND WHAT DO YOU DO WITH THEM
WHEN THEY'RE HERE?

319
00:13:52,875 --> 00:13:54,833
- AKihisa: CRAP!

320
00:13:54,916 --> 00:13:56,000
ILLICIT SEXUAL
RELATIONSHIPS WITH GIRLS

321
00:13:56,083 --> 00:13:57,666
GETS YOU TWO HUNDRED
POINTS TAKEN AWAY.

322
00:13:57,750 --> 00:14:00,625
- ( Akihisa crying helplessly )

323
00:14:00,708 --> 00:14:03,666
- AKIHISA, IT HASN'T BEEN EASY
FOR YOU EITHER, HAS IT?

324
00:14:04,333 --> 00:14:06,041
- YUUJI...

325
00:14:06,125 --> 00:14:08,041
- HOWEVER, I WILL ALLOW ILLICIT
SEXUAL RELATIONSHIPS

326
00:14:08,125 --> 00:14:09,041
WITH BOYS, THOUGH.

327
00:14:09,125 --> 00:14:10,541
- IT'S NOT LIKE THAT!

328
00:14:10,625 --> 00:14:13,416
- IN FACT, I'M GONNA GIVE YOU
TEN POINTS!

329
00:14:13,500 --> 00:14:15,458
- WHAT? LIKE THAT'S SUPPOSED TO
MAKE ME HAPPY?

330
00:14:16,208 --> 00:14:17,916
- HEY, AKIHISA!

331
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,083
SINCE WE CAME HERE UNINVITED,

332
00:14:19,166 --> 00:14:21,041
WE CAN AT LEAST HELP
YOU MAKE DINNER.

333
00:14:21,125 --> 00:14:22,791
- THANKS. THAT'D BE COOL, MAN.

334
00:14:22,875 --> 00:14:24,875
- I CAN HELP.
- MAYBE I COULD COOK!

335
00:14:24,958 --> 00:14:26,625
- ( all gasp )

336
00:14:26,708 --> 00:14:29,000
- NO WAY. WE'LL BE FINE.
YOU STAY HERE.

337
00:14:29,083 --> 00:14:30,875
- YEAH, WE GOT IT.
THANKS FOR OFFERING.

338
00:14:30,958 --> 00:14:32,416
- Mizuki: REALLY? ARE YOU SURE?

339
00:14:32,500 --> 00:14:34,250
- HEY SIS! KEEP 'EM COMPANY.

340
00:14:34,333 --> 00:14:37,333
- SURE. WOULD YOU ALL LIKE TO
SEE SOME OLD PHOTOS OF AKI?

341
00:14:37,416 --> 00:14:38,958
- YEAH, I MEAN IF THAT'S OKAY.

342
00:14:39,041 --> 00:14:40,708
- Akira: LET'S SEE
THE EMBARRASSING ONES FIRST.

343
00:14:40,791 --> 00:14:42,041
- Akihisa: ANYTHING BUT THOSE?

344
00:14:42,125 --> 00:14:43,166
- WE'RE GONNA LIVE.

345
00:14:45,291 --> 00:14:47,208
- SO, THEN,
WHAT ARE WE MAKING?

346
00:14:47,291 --> 00:14:49,583
- LOOKS LIKE WE HAVE EVERYTHING
WE NEED TO MAKE PAELLA.

347
00:14:49,666 --> 00:14:53,000
BELIEVE IT OR NOT,
IT'S ACTUALLY MY FAVORITE DISH.

348
00:14:53,083 --> 00:14:56,083
- CONVENIENT. DID SHE KNOW
WE WERE COMING OVER?

349
00:14:56,166 --> 00:14:58,833
- NO. SHE CAN'T COOK
TO SAVE HER LIFE EITHER.

350
00:14:58,916 --> 00:15:00,750
MUST HAVE BOUGHT TOO MUCH
BY ACCIDENT.

351
00:15:03,625 --> 00:15:05,125
- ( girls laughing )

352
00:15:05,208 --> 00:15:07,083
- Yuuji: YEAH, PUT IT
OVER THERE.

353
00:15:07,166 --> 00:15:10,541
- OKAY, HERE WE GO! THESE ARE
PICTURES OF AKI TAKING A BATH

354
00:15:10,625 --> 00:15:12,000
WHEN HE WAS TWO.

355
00:15:12,083 --> 00:15:15,041
- OH! LOOK, HE'S ADORABLE!

356
00:15:15,125 --> 00:15:18,291
- AND THESE ARE PICTURES OF AKI
TAKING A BATH WHEN HE WAS FOUR.

357
00:15:18,375 --> 00:15:19,875
- Minami: AW, HE FELL ASLEEP!

358
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:24,375
- THESE ARE PICTURES OF AKI
TAKING A BATH WHEN HE WAS SEVEN.

359
00:15:24,458 --> 00:15:27,083
- THIS WAS IN
ELEMENTARY SCHOOL, RIGHT?

360
00:15:27,166 --> 00:15:30,083
- THESE ARE OF AKI TAKING A
BATH WHEN HE WAS TEN YEARS OLD.

361
00:15:30,166 --> 00:15:33,500
- WAIT A SEC! HOW COME I'M
ALWAYS TAKING A BATH?

362
00:15:33,583 --> 00:15:36,666
- THESE ARE OF AKI TAKING A BATH
WHEN HE WAS THIRTEEN.

363
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:38,458
- ( all gasp )

364
00:15:38,541 --> 00:15:40,791
- WAIT. WHY'D YOU ALL GET QUIET?

365
00:15:40,875 --> 00:15:43,791
- AND THESE, ARE OF AKI
TAKING A BATH YESTERDAY.

366
00:15:44,208 --> 00:15:45,833
- NO!

367
00:15:45,916 --> 00:15:47,125
AH! WHEN DID YOU TAKE THOSE?

368
00:15:47,208 --> 00:15:48,416
PLEASE DON'T AT MY
PRIVATE PARTS!

369
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:50,250
PLEASE DON'T LOOK!
PLEASE DON'T LOOK AT THEM!

370
00:15:50,333 --> 00:15:52,208
- Yuuji: COME ON, BATH BOY.
YOU'VE GOT SOME COOKING TO DO.

371
00:15:52,291 --> 00:15:53,333
- Akihisa: NO!

372
00:15:54,625 --> 00:15:55,916
- THIS LOOKS DELICIOUS.

373
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:58,375
- LOOK AT THAT.
YOU MADE PAELLA.

374
00:15:58,458 --> 00:15:59,791
- IS IT OKAY?

375
00:15:59,875 --> 00:16:02,041
I THOUGHT THAT'S WHAT YOU BOUGHT
ALL THOSE GROCERIES FOR.

376
00:16:02,125 --> 00:16:04,375
- IT SMELLS REALLY GOOD, AKI.

377
00:16:04,458 --> 00:16:07,250
- WOW. I HAD NO IDEA YOU
COULD ACTUALLY COOK.

378
00:16:07,333 --> 00:16:09,000
THAT'S SUPER NEAT.

379
00:16:09,083 --> 00:16:10,416
- ( Akihisa screaming
in frustration )

380
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:11,833
HOW DID YOU NOT KNOW?

381
00:16:11,916 --> 00:16:15,291
- OH, NO. AKI'S YELLING AGAIN,
THAT'S NOT VERY NICE.

382
00:16:15,375 --> 00:16:16,500
MINUS TEN POINTS.

383
00:16:16,583 --> 00:16:18,291
IT'S NOT FAIR!
THIS IS ALL YOUR DAMN FAULT!

384
00:16:18,375 --> 00:16:19,625
GAH, WHY DO YOU HATE ME?

385
00:16:19,708 --> 00:16:21,500
IT'S LIKE YOUR DOING YOUR BEST
TO STRESS ME OUT!

386
00:16:21,583 --> 00:16:25,041
- AKI, YOU KNOW AS WELL AS I DO
THAT I COULD NEVER HATE YOU.

387
00:16:25,125 --> 00:16:26,583
- WHAT?

388
00:16:26,666 --> 00:16:28,291
- I CARE ABOUT YOU AS A WOMAN.

389
00:16:28,375 --> 00:16:30,416
- WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

390
00:16:30,500 --> 00:16:33,083
- THERE'S AN OLD, FAMOUS SAYING
THAT GOES LIKE THIS.

391
00:16:33,166 --> 00:16:35,583
THE DUMBER THE CHILD
THE CUTER...

392
00:16:35,666 --> 00:16:37,333
- GIVE IT UP, AKIHISA.

393
00:16:37,416 --> 00:16:38,833
IT SEEMS TO ME SHE
LOVES YOU MORE

394
00:16:38,916 --> 00:16:40,041
THAN ANYONE ELSE IN THE WORLD.

395
00:16:40,125 --> 00:16:42,291
BUT YUUJI, WOULDN'T
THAT MEAN SHE THINKS

396
00:16:42,375 --> 00:16:43,875
I'M THE DUMBEST
PERSON IN THE WORLD?

397
00:16:43,958 --> 00:16:45,041
- SO WHAT IF SHE DOES, AKI?

398
00:16:45,125 --> 00:16:46,416
I HAPPEN TO THINK YOU'RE
THE DUMBEST PERSON

399
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:47,666
IN THE WHOLE WORLD, TOO!

400
00:16:47,750 --> 00:16:49,833
- SO DO I! YOU'RE
STUPIDER THAN ANYONE ELSE

401
00:16:49,916 --> 00:16:51,958
ON THIS ENTIRE PLANET
IN MY OPINION!

402
00:16:52,041 --> 00:16:54,125
- STOP IT! WHY ARE YOU
GOING OUT OF YOUR WAY

403
00:16:54,208 --> 00:16:55,375
TO HURT MY PRECIOUS FEELINGS!

404
00:16:55,458 --> 00:16:57,041
- WOW, YOU REALLY ARE AN IDIOT.

405
00:16:58,875 --> 00:17:02,750
- OKAY, NOW THAT DINNER'S
FINALLY OVER, WE SHOULD STUDY.

406
00:17:02,833 --> 00:17:06,250
- IF YOU'D LIKE, I CAN HELP
ALL OF YOU. I REALLY DON'T MIND.

407
00:17:06,333 --> 00:17:08,375
- ARE YOU SURE?

408
00:17:08,458 --> 00:17:10,666
- I WENT TO SCHOOL OVERSEAS
AND GOT A DEGREE IN EDUCATION,

409
00:17:10,750 --> 00:17:12,541
SO I'M KIND OF TRAINED FOR IT.

410
00:17:12,625 --> 00:17:13,666
- WHERE OVERSEAS?

411
00:17:13,750 --> 00:17:15,375
- JUST IN BOSTON, MASSACHUSETTS.

412
00:17:15,458 --> 00:17:18,750
- Yuuji: YOU'RE KIDDING ME. DO
YOU MEAN... SHE WENT TO HARVARD?

413
00:17:18,833 --> 00:17:21,166
- ( Minami, Mizuki gasp )
- INTERESTING...

414
00:17:21,250 --> 00:17:22,333
SHE GOT THE GOOD GENES.

415
00:17:22,416 --> 00:17:24,750
- WHAT'S THAT SUPPOSED TO MEAN,
YOU, JERK?

416
00:17:24,833 --> 00:17:27,791
- LOOK WHAT I FOUND
UNDER AKI'S BED TODAY.

417
00:17:27,875 --> 00:17:29,833
THEY MUST BE FOR
REFERENCE PURPOSES.

418
00:17:29,916 --> 00:17:32,541
- Akihisa: BUT THOSE ARE MY
ULTIMATE OF TOP SECRET SECRETS!

419
00:17:32,625 --> 00:17:35,208
- UNFORTUNATELY, I'M GOING TO
HAVE TO TAKE AWAY SIXTY POINTS.

420
00:17:35,291 --> 00:17:37,458
- SO, YOU'RE SUBTRACTING
TEN POINTS PER BOOK?

421
00:17:37,541 --> 00:17:38,625
- NO. YOU'RE LOSING POINTS

422
00:17:38,708 --> 00:17:40,375
FOR NOT HAVING DIRTY BOOKS
ABOUT SISTERS.

423
00:17:40,458 --> 00:17:43,041
- NO! IS THERE NO END?
THIS IS BRUTAL!

424
00:17:43,125 --> 00:17:45,833
- THEY LOOK LIKE PHYS. ED
REFERENCES TO ME.

425
00:17:45,916 --> 00:17:49,000
- STOP! I CAN'T SHARE THOSE
WITH THEM, THEY'VE BEEN USED!

426
00:17:49,083 --> 00:17:53,000
- AKI TENDS TO STUDY BY FOCUSING
ON VERY SPECIFIC SUBJECTS.

427
00:17:53,083 --> 00:17:55,166
APPARENTLY HE LIKES THE
SUBJECT OF GIRLS

428
00:17:55,250 --> 00:17:57,666
WITH BIG BREASTS AND PONYTAILS.

429
00:17:59,916 --> 00:18:02,958
- ALL RIGHT THEN. LET'S GET TO
THAT STUDYING, SHALL WE?

430
00:18:03,041 --> 00:18:05,458
- AND JUST WHAT ARE YOU
DOING TO YOUR HAIR, MIZUKI?

431
00:18:05,541 --> 00:18:07,875
- I THOUGHT I'D JUST TIE IT BACK
SO IT DOESN'T GET IN MY WAY.

432
00:18:07,958 --> 00:18:09,541
- OH, HERE!
I CAN DO IT FOR YOU!.

433
00:18:09,625 --> 00:18:12,083
- OW! YOU'RE HURTING ME, MINAMI,
PLEASE STOP THE PAIN!.

434
00:18:12,166 --> 00:18:13,875
- I DON'T NEED YOU TO HELP ME!
- WAIT A SECOND.

435
00:18:13,958 --> 00:18:16,500
YOUR HAIR DOESN'T
NORMALLY GET IN YOUR WAY.

436
00:18:16,583 --> 00:18:18,708
- ANOTHER ONE HUNDRED POINTS
TO BE DEDUCTED.

437
00:18:18,791 --> 00:18:21,208
- WHAT? HOW COME?

438
00:18:21,291 --> 00:18:22,375
- TRUST ME, LITTLE BROTHER.

439
00:18:22,458 --> 00:18:24,833
ONE OF THESE DAYS, YOU'LL
UNDERSTAND WHY.

440
00:18:28,083 --> 00:18:30,458
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT, MAN?
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING FOR?

441
00:18:30,541 --> 00:18:32,916
- THE OTHER ONE THOUSAND NINE
HUNDRED NINETY-FOUR BOOKS.

442
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:34,708
- YOU THOUGHT I WAS SERIOUS?

443
00:18:36,791 --> 00:18:38,541
- Mizuki: HEY THERE.
GOOD MORNING, YOSHII.

444
00:18:38,625 --> 00:18:40,125
- Minami: WHAT'S UP, AKI?

445
00:18:41,375 --> 00:18:43,000
- HEY GIRLS. MORNING.

446
00:18:43,083 --> 00:18:44,833
DID YOU CHANGE YOUR HAIR
STYLE, HIMEJI?

447
00:18:44,916 --> 00:18:48,583
- OH, YES. I JUST WANTED
SOMETHING DIFFERENT.

448
00:18:48,666 --> 00:18:50,833
- DID YOU CHANGE YOUR
BOOB STYLE, MINAMI?

449
00:18:50,916 --> 00:18:53,333
- NO WAY!
THEY JUST GREW OVER NIGHT!

450
00:18:53,416 --> 00:18:54,458
- SERIOUSLY?

451
00:18:54,541 --> 00:18:56,916
- YES, SERIOUSLY.
I'M STILL GROWING.

452
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:59,041
- ( popping sound )

453
00:18:59,125 --> 00:19:01,083
- CAN'T ALLOW YOU TO
DISGRACE THE FEMALE BREAST

454
00:19:01,166 --> 00:19:02,666
WITH SUCH IMPERTINENCE.

455
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:03,875
- ( Minami growls )

456
00:19:06,041 --> 00:19:07,916
- YESTERDAY WAS FUN, WASN'T IT?

457
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:10,041
- WE MANAGED TO GET
SOME STUDYING DONE, TOO.

458
00:19:10,125 --> 00:19:12,666
- YEAH, BUT IT LOOKS LIKE I
WON'T BE ALLOWED TO LIVE ALONE.

459
00:19:12,750 --> 00:19:14,958
I WISH SHE'D GO BACK TO AMERICA.

460
00:19:15,041 --> 00:19:17,500
- YOU SHOULDN'T TALK THAT WAY
ABOUT YOUR FAMILY.

461
00:19:17,583 --> 00:19:19,458
- Yuuji: SHE SEEMED
PRETTY COOL TO ME.

462
00:19:19,541 --> 00:19:20,791
- YEAH, RIGHT.

463
00:19:20,875 --> 00:19:23,416
SHE ALWAYS TAKES AWAY POINTS AND
TRIES TO KISS ME.

464
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:25,958
